Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在祥子姐姐大人家召开新年会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还仅限女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  谢谢您的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会去拜访的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父母都同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也打电话给由乃同学和志摩子同学确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也给瞳子寄邀请函了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没先过问祐巳你  请你原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样也无所谓才寄出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得就这样什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子会越离越远的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定傻眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我要大家静静守护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却最先开始管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然如此了解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是什么超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是你的姐姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我这么做没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清子阿姨会开心地收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安  祐巳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人  请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得很对不起祐巳大人您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如今旧事重提  也只能再三道歉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你指瞳子的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直期望瞳子能做祐巳大人的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:08:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是觉得祐巳大人能认瞳子她做妹妹就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我却以为祐巳大人您完全不把瞳子当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  当祐巳大人您无意地干预瞳子的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到很厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您一定认真地考虑过瞳子的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她拒绝成为姐妹一事  并无所谓对错之分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  我认为欺骗自己的感情算不上好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来乃梨子你认为瞳子不讨厌我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是我做错了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做错了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时机啊地点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或是表达方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  是我们来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道两位今年是初次见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我离远一点  你们慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都这么熟了何必介意这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  令大人和由乃大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们说会直接过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是公园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令她们已经到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…接下来嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学  令大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清子阿姨  祐巳同学她们来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  难得你们都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳你都记得啊  太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今年也请大家多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无酒精的也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就开动合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了些忙肚子早饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和小令带的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…她现在做着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是寿司店的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是同一时间来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能会来吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我开始唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}なげきつつ　ひとりぬる夜の　あくるまは…{\r}\N长叹独眠夜漫漫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,右大将道纲母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（藤原道纲母：平安中期的歌人。百人一首第53号全文是\N「なげきつつ　ひとりぬる夜の　あくるまは　いかに久しき　ものとかはしる」\N(「拾遗和歌集」恋四·912)中文翻译：长叹独眠夜漫漫，长待天明君不知。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正确  志摩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}いにしへの{\r}\N古都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}いにしへ　いにしへ…{\r}\N古都…古都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a10}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs17}奈良の都の…{\r}\N奈良…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊势大辅之歌  正确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（伊势大辅：平安中期女流歌人。百人一首第61号全文是\N「いにしへの　奈良の都の　八重桜　けふ九重に　匂ひぬるかな」\N(「词花集」春29)中文翻译：古都奈良八重樱，今日红满九重门。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}没错  几乎和祥子一样厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我几乎都抢不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起去年努力了不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:28.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a9\pos(662,5)\frz-90\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs20}（注释 : 这张是第一首 ，天智天皇作 。\N「秋の田の　仮庵の庵の　苫をあらみ\N我が衣手は　露に濡れつつ」的后句 。\N中文翻译 : 秋日田圃粗庵內 ，夜露湿濡吾衣袖 。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都是些钻牛角尖的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:32.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（由左到右分别为，\N{\fs17}　　　　　　君がため　惜しからざりし　命さへ　长くもがなと　思ひけるかな。{\r}\N藤原义孝：往昔不顾抛此身，如今为你祈长生。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}　　　　　　　　　　永らへば　また此顷や　しのばれむ　忧しと见し世ぞ　今は恋しき。{\r}\N（藤原清辅朝臣：未来此身如长在，会否笑看今日苦。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}　　　　　　风をいたみ　岩うつ波の　おのれのみ　くだけてものを　思ふころかな。{\r}\N（源重之：冽风激浪击岸岩，唯我心若浪四逬。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17}　　　恨みわび　ほさぬ袖だに　あるものを　恋に朽ちなむ　名こそ惜しけれ。{\r}\N（相模：恨别衣袖久未干，更惜名声为爱贱。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真伤人脑筋呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,百人一首占卜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但照这种说法  像志摩子拿到这么多张的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铁定喜怒哀乐都混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一片混乱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来玩「真人双六」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（双六：在纸上所划的格子内掷骰子然后移动棋子的游戏。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真人双六？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  以两人为一组对战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分组就按照蔷薇的颜色来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩家本身代替棋子来移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每间房间都写上了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请按指示来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我丢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三是…水蚤之间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水蚤？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是设在二楼的和室  祥子就太占便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方这么用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五是河马之间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是振袖鱼之间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（振袖鱼：振袖为日本女性和服形式之一，而多斑扇尾鱼因像之而得名。）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孔雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水蚤在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（鸵鸟之间）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来点数与到房间的距离没有关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是振袖鱼之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是要我们做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想指令都会是「穿上这里的和服」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不一定要是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种麻烦任务理应由妹妹来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  我穿的话仅是换了身颜色不同的和服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  乖乖地脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等啊  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起码先把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家里只有女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（给妹妹穿上振袖）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢夸奬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有队伍都完成了最初的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（河马之间）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真人双六继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边为还穿不习惯的腰带而难受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边完成了接下来的几项指令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  我们红蔷薇组获得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:30.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（达成）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}明明很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都能来真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定大家在初二时原本是有别的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却调整了自己的时间聚集到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很明白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也晓得制造这机会的是姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把这件事深深烙印在心底的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻  可以不用顾虑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是自己人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学  清子阿姨说等下要刷抹茶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把垃圾给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会如此幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中还是会吹进冰冷的风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是你关错整理心情的房门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是「虽然很幸福但心中还是会吹进冰冷的风」之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我病得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在你们俩面前自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和朋友的房间如此充实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一间却空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会有种失落感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一间是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没那种房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近为了瞳子  扩建起房子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然造起了房间  却没有妹妹入住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风透过缝隙吹进了祐巳同学你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说是理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样  别担心自己哪里出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟说了佳句的我  也正在施工扩建啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人心是房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想就很好理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而姐姐大人和我的房子是如此充实多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  在睡之前还是要放上这个才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}（なかきよ：此歌实为「宝船之歌」，回文歌与言灵的一种，为日本初梦文化一环\N于室町时传开，习俗上于初二或初三将歌写在七福神宝船绘纸上压在枕下，咏三遍而枕。）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,写上长夜的诗句放在枕头下就这样睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了能做个好初梦的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得你记住了呢  祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:29.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}{\a9\pos(690,5)\frz-90\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs20}（人醒长夜沈睡中  乘浪宝船鸣佳音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我关灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这睡脸真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对好友的妹妹感觉都如此地强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果换作是自己的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的初梦果不期然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于她  瞳子的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子在我房间旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  毛玻璃遮挡着在我们之间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看瞳子的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了瞳子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边也擦一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然这雾气是不会散的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学  你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做错了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你就不能理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子  拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快往这边看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢贵府的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们过得十分愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见瞳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想认瞳子做妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想了解瞳子的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去柏木学长家看看吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要问柏木学长也许就能了解瞳子更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…或许会让瞳子不快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反而更加封闭内心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是不会做出这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有资格被她叫姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也做不到  就这样开始了新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安  祐巳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵…贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像去年…我们之间什么也没发生似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像忘却了一切似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小令  千万不能放手哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在教我学骑自行车的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小令明明这么答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  却在绝妙的时机放开了手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.19,0:24:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在寒假  菜菜和小令切磋完剑道之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃在为菜菜加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小令回答「这样就行了」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.37,0:24:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一回  「假面的女演员」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.97,0:24:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学跟我一样  也有另一段辛酸的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:35.14,biaoti1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(521,288)}假 面 的 女 演 员
